pr_body:
Hello all,

This pr is about my GSoC 2021 project, call hierarchy support. I create a draft to show my progress to those who may be interested.

**Progress**

- [x] Prepare call hierarchy (working now)
- [x] Incoming calls
- [x] Outgoing calls

**Known issues**

- [x] Data family range error (see commented test)
- [x] Incoming/Outgoing test missing
- [x] Name display not optimized for `DuplicateRecordFields`
